{"tid":2097022,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"WhatsApp周一發聲明稱言論自由是基本人權，因《國安法》的影響，已暫停香港執法機構索取用戶數據的要求","createTime":"2020-07-06T13:46:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-06T14:09:18.000Z","uid":230104,"like":43,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"bb81b2ea8f97905e906f9dde364d002137344ed0","tid":2097022,"uid":230104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T13:46:46.000Z","msg":"facebook發言人回覆查詢表示： 「facebook深信言論自由是基本人權，我們支持所有人都可在毋須擔心自身安全和其他顧慮的情況下有權利表達自己的想法。此外，我們對政府的請求有一套全球一致的處理方式，一律以facebook政策、當地法律及國際人權標準作為考量準則。我們目前已決定暫停檢視政府對索取香港用戶資料的請求，並就《香港特別行政區維護國家安全法》作進一步法律評估，同時會將人權法準則及國際人權法專家的意見納入考慮範圍。」<br />\n<br />\n（路透社/明報記者）"},{"pid":"65486975d1b2facd807cb25f421cb0248ea09a4e","tid":2097022,"uid":249885,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T13:49:16.000Z","msg":"信住先 suckerberg"},{"pid":"8a806b70f613409bdde513d3d7f58675f6781925","tid":2097022,"uid":77196,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T13:50:13.000Z","msg":"豬西伯格信得過咩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d71834848eba13210e1e458dd6484a95fda805e","tid":2097022,"uid":267494,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T13:50:32.000Z","msg":"係至好，港共唔會跪<br />\n最好whatsapp同facebook自已中斷香港服務<br />\n不過我睇死豬閪唔會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c0dfaec61650331902f7b8fd92dc96f7c6388b9","tid":2097022,"uid":26050,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T13:50:40.000Z","msg":"ok用43條告到去美國"},{"pid":"256fe6c14fc64d3706b0e3019360e8b36137d28b","tid":2097022,"uid":230104,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"8a806b70f613409bdde513d3d7f58675f6781925","tid":2097022,"uid":77196,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T13:50:13.000Z","msg":"豬西伯格信得過咩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T13:50:41.000Z","msg":"隻老婆奴信唔過"},{"pid":"8fc1b67e80a688b86272b154ba4